    PropertyValueSource, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​NamedObject>
    public class NameMap<NamedObject extends Named>
extends BaseStringMap<NamedObject>
    A map to look up Named objects by their name. Objects can be added to the map with add(Named) instead of put() and their name will be used as the map key. To retrieve a value, get(Name) or get(String) can be called. Map keys are case-insensitive by default. If case sensitivity is desired, caseSensitive(boolean) can be used.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
